Package: open-vm-modules-2.6.31-1-amd64-vyatta
Architecture: amd64
Provides: open-vm-modules
Recommends: open-vm-tools
Replaces: open-vm-tools-2.6.31-1-amd64-vyatta
Depends: linux-image-2.6.31-1-amd64-vyatta
Description: Vyatta version of the open-vm modules for amd64
 This package provides the accelerated drivers vyatta on VMWare for kernel
 linux-image-2.6.31-1-amd64-vyatta.

Package: open-vm-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: libc6,  libglib2.0-0
Description: tools and components for VMware guest systems (CLI tools)
 The Open Virtual Machine Tools (open-vm-tools) are the open source
 implementation of VMware Tools. They are a set of guest operating system
 Virtualization components that enhance performance and user experience of
 virtual machines.

